\pard\plain \fi0\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Several dozen hundred years in the future of some planet a lone explorer has gotten lost due to a freakish accident during a routine flight test refueling.\~ Phineas G. Willowman, Space Ranger, will discover that everything has already happened and will happen again (so at least he'll get to experience it) in the meantime he has to save the Universe from the evil octopus Harold at the center of the galaxy (explains all the arms), save the girl and keep his dog Harley (a handsome if slightly excitable Australian Terrier) from peeing in the ship.\~ Again.}
