\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Describe it.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \line }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Take the television shows Farscape, Stargate: Atlantis and Battlestar Galactica, the Hitchikers Guide the Galaxy books and Greek mythology (actually, any mythology is fair game.\~ (Double actually, it doesn't even have to be mythology)) take out the boring bits, put the rest in a box, shake it up, dump it out on the table and put it all back together at random to form a story and you'll have a good idea of what it's like. At least you would if I had thought of that before I started writing it.\~}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \line }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 In fact your better off just tossing all of it out the window and giving typewriters to a bunch of Dashounds and letting them have at it.\~ That's what I did anyway.}
